'''天主教曼弗雷多尼亚-维耶斯泰-圣乔凡尼罗通多总教区'''是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[意大利|意大利]]南部[[普利亚|普利亚]]大区设立的一个教区。1074年西旁托教区升格为总教区（曼弗雷多尼亚毁于地震的古城）。1818年与维耶斯泰教区合并。2002年圣乔凡尼罗通多教区并入<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dmavi.html |title=''Catholic Hierarchy'' page |access-date=2008-10-27 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201204149/https://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dmavi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現任總主教為{{link-it|方濟各·莫斯科內|Franco Moscone}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 03.11.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/03/181103b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717090445/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/03/181103b.html |archivedate=2019-07-17 |language=en |date=2018-11-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

